rapid2STORM v1.3 - dSTORM analysis and data acquisition software
PicoQuant GmbH - Dec. 2009


Note:
=====
If a network license was purchased, the software installation of the
Hardlock drivers for each client terminal is identical to the installation
described below, whereas the Hardlock network module must be connected
to a computer, which is network-accessible from all PCs, which will run the
rapid2STORM software. For this computer the Hardlock driver installation
is different from the usual procedure. Please refer to the documentation
in the subfolder Hardlock\Network and contact your network administrator 
if necessary.

